  ('reading', '1', 2, '1.read', 'ELA.1.R.1', 'Read: "Mia planted a seed. She gave it water and sun. Soon a flower grew." What did Mia grow?', '["A bug","A tree","A rock","A flower"]', 3, 'The seed Mia watered grew into a flower.', 10),
